                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6761" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0464</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8529 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“京”心培养，“博”出未来：师徒制实践何以历久弥新？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Cultivating elaborately of &quot;Jing&quot;, creating the future with &quot;bo&quot;: How does the practice of mentoring last for a long time?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曾颢，赵曙明（通讯作者），瞿皎姣，王风，罗焰，余薇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西科技师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东京博控股集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">维修部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">京博石化；师带徒；师徒关系；组织社会化；运行机制；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Jingbo Petrochemical; mentoring; mentoring relationship; organizational socialization; operating mechanism</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">师徒制作为人力资源开发的重要工具之一，对员工组织社会化具有积极影响。本案例以山东京博石油化工有限公司（简称：京博石化）运行保障集合车间主任阎晓青对师徒制的困惑为起点，在梳理京博石化师徒制历史沿革的基础上，描述了运行保障集合车间通过专业课题、系列活动、大学生提升团队等方式对师徒制进行探索和变革，从而师带徒运行机制不断创新，焕发新生的过程。本案例旨在引导学生通过分析京博石化运行保障车间的师徒制实践，学习师徒制的概念、功能；掌握组织社会化理论，并引导学生从自我决定理论视角去理解师徒制对新员工组织社会化的影响过程。通过案例学习进一步帮助学生认识员工组织社会化现实意义，并为企业的师徒制管理实践提供一定借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Mentoring, as one of the important tools in human resource development, has a positive impact on the socialization of employee organizations. This case starts with Yan Xiaoqing, director of the operation guarantee collection workshop of Shandong Dongbo Petrochemical Co., Ltd. (abbreviation: Jingbo Petrochemical), who is confused about the mentoring system. On the basis of sorting out the history of Jingbo Petrochemical&#39;s mentoring system, this case describes the whole process that the operation guarantee collection workshop explores and reforms the mentoring system through professional topics, series of activities, and college students&#39; promotion team, so as to continuously improve the operating mechanism of the mentoring system and rejuvenate it. This case aims to guide students to learn the concept and function of mentoring and master the theory of organizational socialization by analyzing the practice of mentoring in the operation guarantee workshop of Jingbo Petrochemical, and guide students to understand the impact of mentoring on the organizational socialization of new employees from the perspective of self determination theory. Through case study, students can further understand the practical significance of employee organization socialization and provide some reference for the practice of mentoring system.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">师徒制的概念及功能；组织社会化理论；高质量师徒关系特征；自我决定理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
